2.1.name: wordpress/listpipe
2.1.description: ListPipe is a blog service that provides Powerful Custom Content written just for you. We use the ListPipe Content Generator to deliver your subscription content into your blog. The plugin we discuss on this page provides a secure, account-specific handshake with our content service and allows us to deliver your content directly to your blog. Please note that you must INSTALL and ACTIVATE (installing the plugin without activating it is not sufficient) the ListPipe plugin for WordPress to receive content from ListPipe (you should INSTALL and ACTIVATE the ListPipe plugin for WordPress before you create your ListPipe account). If you do not intend to start a ListPipe account, then this plugin will be of no use to you.
